author: @jolbrias1
content: She had such a great sense of humor about it. I saw this tour July 9, 2024 in Boston & during my show she had an incident and they had to come fix something on her. I don’t remember what it was and she started laughing during that too The younger Madonna would’ve been furious if there was any mistakes in the show but you can see what a great sense of humor she has now, and she never stop singing
